border-radius: var(--radius);
background-color: rgba(60, 90, 180, 0.05);

fr:mainmatter.html:div:
Example. 
  There is an actual dependency between instructions here that cannot be circumvented by OoO hardware 
for (i = 0; i < n; i++)
    sum += a[i];
However, this can be re-written at the software level to get some parallelism within loop bodies as:
for (i = 0; i < n; i += 4) {
    s0 += a[i];   s1 += a[i+1];
    s2 += a[i+2]; s3 += a[i+3];
}
sum = (s0 + s1) + (s2 + s3);}
